Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:15.34,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(2338,2338,\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}hey, 運命が呼んでいる{\fscx50} {\fscx100}for the big stage
