Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:34.69,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I sing through the heartbreak{\fscx50} {\fscx100}信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.61,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}光が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.07,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I've got you You've got me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:44.37,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最後まで進んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:48.37,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Oh in the night we can wish on a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}光の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.97,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}手を伸ばし続けた{\fscx50} {\fscx100}big dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.64,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰かの目には{\fscx50} {\fscx100}it's a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.81,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}“All the stars that shine brightest, Burn out the fastest”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:08.14,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ぼくら越えていける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:11.40,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰も知らない{\fscx50} {\fscx100}tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:15.28,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}心の声だけ{\fscx50} {\fscx100}follow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.90,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}駆け抜けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.74,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}夢と未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}重なるように
